a-size-base 3: Found these while browsing Amazon's pet section, looking for a treat for Sukie, our family dog who is 8.5 year old now. Sukie was super energetic when she was in her puppy stage, and loved treats that she could spend some time chewing on. However, with the age, she grew out of it and it felt like she was uninterested no matter the efforts we made to find something appealing to her.As soon as I opened the bag and gave her a Senior Dental Ring, she sniffed, bit, and ran away with the treat! We think she was hiding it for later, to enjoy peacefully when nobody was around. I've never seen her getting so excited about a treat in these past few years, this was such a surprise! I'm happy we finally found something that she loves, and allows us to get a glimpse of the little playful puppy she used to be!
